      <span style="font-size:11px;color:#a0aec0;font-weight:400">25FW·26SS · 소진율 70%↑ · 재고 30개↓ · 커버낫 C-prefix 제외</span>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-body">
      <div class="tbl-wrap">
        <table class="data-table"><thead><tr>
          <th>브랜드</th><th>시즌</th><th>품번</th><th>품명</th><th>품목</th>
          <th class="num-r">발주</th><th class="num-r">누계입고</th><th class="num-r">누계판매</th>
          <th class="num-r">소진율</th><th class="num-r">총재고</th><th class="num-r">물류/매장</th>
        </tr></thead><tbody id="alarmBody"></tbody></table>
      </div>
      <p class="note">빨간 행: 소진율 85%↑ &nbsp;|&nbsp; 노란 행: 70~84%</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ⑤ 판매 상위 + 가방 현년 vs 전년 비교 -->
  <div class="section">
    <div class="sec-header">
      <span>📈 판매 상위 비교 — 이번기간 vs 전년동기</span>
      <div class="mode-toggle">
        <button class="mode-btn active" data-sm="26ss" onclick="setSpikeMode(this)">26SS</button>
        <button class="mode-btn"        data-sm="all"  onclick="setSpikeMode(this)">재고포함</button>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="sec-body">

      <!-- 전체 판매 상위 -->
      <div style="margin-bottom:16px">
        <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:8px">전체 품목 판매상위</div>
        <div class="tbl-wrap">
          <table class="data-table"><thead><tr>
            <th>브랜드</th><th>시즌</th><th>품번</th><th>품명</th><th>품목</th>
            <th class="num-r">이번기간</th><th class="num-r">전주</th><th class="num-r">증감</th>
            <th class="num-r">기간매출</th><th class="num-r">소진율</th><th class="num-r">총재고</th>
          </tr></thead><tbody id="spikeBody"></tbody></table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 가방 현년 vs 전년 좌우 비교 -->
      <div style="font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:#4a5568;margin-bottom:8px">
        가방 판매상위 — 현년 vs 전년 비교
      </div>
      <div class="compare-grid">
        <!-- 현년 -->
        <div class="compare-panel">
          <div class="panel-header">
            <span class="panel-year-cur">현년 이번기간</span>
            <span id="curSeasonLabel" style="font-size:11px;color:#a0aec0"></span>
          </div>
          <div class="panel-body">
            <table class="data-table"><thead><tr>
              <th class="num-r" style="width:28px">#</th>
              <th>품번</th><th>품명</th><th>품목</th>
              <th class="num-r">기간판매</th><th class="num-r">누계판매</th>
              <th class="num-r">소진율</th><th class="num-r">재고</th>
            </tr></thead><tbody id="bagCurBody"></tbody></table>
